<figureCitation box="[791,884,1296,1322]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="14.[189,232,1920,1946]" captionTargetBox="[213,1391,1084,1845]" captionTargetId="figure-245@14.[189,1398,1084,1881]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="Fig. 8. Male metaleg, lateral view. A. Merodon funestus (Fabricius, 1794) (CWM; FSUNS 10347). B. M. vittatus Vujić &amp; Likov sp. nov., holotype (NBCN; FSUNS ID 04085). Calcar on metatrochanter marked with arrow. Scale bar = 2 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5013024" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5013024/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="93">Fig. 8A</figureCitation>
